                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                          <td><strong>RAM</strong></td>
                          <td>2GB 133MHz ECC</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                          <td><strong>Hard disks</strong></td>
                          <td>2x 250GB IDE</td>
                        </tr>
                      </tbody>
                    </table>
                    <p>
                      This server has seen use before, but we‚Äôve replaced all
                      the moving parts; we‚Äôre quite pleased with its condition,
                      and think it will provide us with a number of years of
                      good service. And, we hope that we don‚Äôt need to do a
